{
  "title": "Dreamy Spicy Algerian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A jammy and springy Algerian dish featuring jalapeno and ferment, perfect for a lazy Sunday, this keto-friendly tagine is a hearty and flavorful stew.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
